# Eggnog

Based on [A Luxurious and Strong Eggnog Recipe](https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/voraciously/wp/2019/12/11/a-luxurious-and-strong-eggnog-recipe-to-sustain-you-through-this-holiday-season-and-many-more/) in the Washington Post

